response.mean: Noun: A hard rigid usually large covering of an animal.; The outside part of a fruit or seed.; Something like an external structure that resembles a shell.; A casing without substance.; The hard exterior of an egg.; A hard enclosing cover.Verb: To take out of the shell.; To fall out of the shell.; To cast the external covering.; To gather shells from a beach.
